  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for python-python-engineio",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for python-python-engineio fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2026-48802: remote user can cause the creation of unnecessary background\n  threads in the server through the heartbeat mechanism and cause a DoS \n  (bsc#1269544).\n- CVE-2026-48809: size of incoming messages is not checked before they are loaded\n  into memory and allows remote users to cause a DoS via excessive memory allocation\n  (bsc#1269545).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
